祝你好运，玛丽

1085
01:28:32,139 --> 01:28:33,640
- Oh.
哦

1086
01:28:43,776 --> 01:28:45,527
- I wish you every
success and happiness
我希望你成功和幸福

1087
01:28:45,528 --> 01:28:47,238
in America, princess.
在美洲，公主

